metadata.name: Lady Godiva ✿
metadata.description:
Lady godiva is an aristocratic woman. who are brave and sacrifice for the people

It is regarded as one of the real and beautiful legends.

I got to know lady godiva from Nanaminvestor. I was very moved by this legend. And it made me want to draw this picture to the best of my ability.

Really thank you for introducing me many good and fun legends ♥
